message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "lsm-bloom-allocation: the value of adaptivity in LSM Bloom-filter tuning"
authors:
  - family-names: Mandarapu
    given-names: Madhulatha
    email: madhulatha@samyama.ai
